<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.5">
<l>avvav viṭampukkav vāyarpeṇ ṭirkkaṇuk kaṉāy</l>
<l>kovvaik kaṉivāy koṭuttukkū ḻaimaicey yāmē</l>
<l>evvum cilaiyuṭai vēṭarkā ṉiṭaikkaṉ ṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>teyvat talaivaṉaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To stop him from entering this and that place</l>
<l rend="indent">as one who is intimate with the women of those shepherds,</l>
<l>giving [them his] kovvai fruit lips and caressing [them],</l>
<l>I sent the leader of the gods after the calves in the forest</l>
<l rend="indent">with hunters who have bows that cause pain.</l>
<l>Ah! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
